Introduction

Dai Meng is a Chinese idol singer. She graduated from the Chinese idol group SNH48 (Team SII) and is an active member of its sub-unit, 7SENSES, under STAR48.

In 2020, she participated in the Chinese idol survival show Youth With You 2 and ranked 15th.

On July 16, 2023, Dai Meng announced on her official Weibo account that on July 7, 2023, she had filed a lawsuit against her company, Siba Media, and had applied for labor dispute arbitration. She also stated that due to this lawsuit having an NDA, she cannot share more information with fans about where she stands or her future with Siba Media and STAR48.
